Text: As the US Fed debates its next rate announcement tomorrow, a liquidity crunch in overnight lending rates in the repo market prompted the NY Fed to inject $53b into the US banking system today.
Cause: As the US Fed debates its next rate announcement tomorrow, a liquidity crunch in overnight lending rates in the repo market
Effect: the NY Fed to inject $53b into the US banking system today.
